# Aksay, Republic of Dagestan

}}
Aksay (; , Yaxsay) is a rural locality (a selo) in Khasavyurtovsky District, Republic of Dagestan, Russia. Population:  There are 88 streets. Aksay is located on both sides of the Aksay river.
Geography
Aksay is located 21&nbsp;km northwest of Khasavyurt (the district's administrative centre) by road. Adzhimazhagatyurt is the nearest rural locality.
